idea. You're not trying to sell an idea that's false, right? That's what a good salesperson does

00:09:31.799 --> 00:09:37.719
is try and figure out what's the problem that you have. Do I have something that is valuable to you

00:09:37.719 --> 00:09:42.919
that can solve that problem and that you're willing to kind of expend money or time or something for?

00:09:43.880 --> 00:09:49.640
So always be selling is another kind of mantra of no matter what you're doing, you're marketing

